Installation
============

Ubuntu:
apt-get install python-dev
apt-get install python-setuptools
easy_install twisted
easy_install ecdsa
apt-get install python-twisted-words

Configuration
=============

Copy settings.sample.py to settings.py
Edit at least this values: HOSTNAME, BITCOIN_TRUSTED_*

Startup
=======
Start devel server:
twistd -ny server.tac

Devel server *without* lowlevel messages of Twisted:
twistd -ny server.tac -l log/twistd.log
 
